.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-REGEX 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
regex \- Test a regex pattern against text
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBregex\fR [\fB\-\-flags\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIPATTERN\fR> [\fITEXT\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Test a regex pattern against text
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-flags\fR \fI<FLAGS>\fR [default: g]
Flags: g (find all), i (case\-insensitive), m (multi\-line), s (dot\-all), x (extended)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIPATTERN\fR>
Regex pattern (Rust regex syntax)
.TP
[\fITEXT\fR]
Text to match (or path / stdin)
